Name: There is No Stairs
About the game: There Is No Stairs Another pain here...No, there is a platformer game. Follow the bird who stole the blueprint! Although there are no stairs in the world, a reliable rocket launcher is with you instead. ◇ Aim Under Your Feet and Shoot ◇ Jump higher and farther with the recoil of a rocket explosion! ◇ Go After That [s]Freaking[/s] Pigeon Bird! ◇ The timing of exquisite aiming and jumping is the key to success. ◇ Progress Is Not Saved. ◇ Feel how much you're improving every time you fall! ◇ If you can get the blueprint back, this year's Bonel Award will be yours! 'Isn't it faster to draw a blueprint again?' - Assistant A.
